---
description: Creative generation quality gate
globs:
  - "**/*"
alwaysApply: false
---

Use Creative Generation Ultrawork for image, logo, favicon, video, audio, and asset-analysis work.

Before handoff, create run-scoped docs under `.opendock/runs/creative-gen/<run-id>/` from `.opendock/templates/creative-gen/`, update the run `brief.md` and `manifest.md`, and run:

```bash
opendock verify-hook opendock/creative-gen-ultrawork .opendock/harness/opendock__creative-gen-ultrawork/check.mjs
```
